# Week 3 exercise

-Welcome to the virtual pet shelter (a no-kill shelter). 
-you can admit a pet by giving us their name and description
-you'll find some pets already in the shelter. Some are more hungry or messy than others
-you'll need to periodically feed, water, and clean individual cages to keep the pets happy
-you can adopt a pet at any time (but make sure it's going to a good home!)
-don't forget to play with the pets to keep them from being too bored
-watch out for Old Gregg. He drinks Bailey's from a shoe.
-have fun!